name: UNCEASING VIXEN 22:10
description: She hugs herself because hugs are such fickle things. If the embrace of another can’t warm you, then you love on yourself. Her arms wrap herself to keep the vixen at bay. The unceasing nature of her persuasion is enough to lure any man into an abyss of surreal euphoria. The treasures of life are stowed away in a secret vault, far beneath the stacks of vengeance in one’s ego. Her pneuma was forever displayed for the masses, drunk on seduction and sophisticated passion. In the moments of the day, she sings a silent song, but you hear her emphatically.
